1.3 Definitions, Acronyms, and Abbreviations

	"Player", for the purposes of this document, will refer to the human user of the program.
	"Client", by contrast, will refer to the program itself, typically in relation to the
	server to which the program is designed to connect.
	
1.4 References

	Hanabi is the card game which is being referred to in this document.  It is assumed that
	the reader will know how the game itself is played, but a copy of the game rules can be
